source.name: Office of Adoption and Child Custody Advocacy - Performance Measures Adoption Investigations  2010
source.description: The department is court ordered to complete a home investigation to determine if potential adoptive family whom is seeking permanency is suitable for placement.  The Program Objectives are to provide critical information to the court in a timely manner
